\date{2025-01-09}
\title{Integer Partition}
\taxon{theorem}

\p{
  Denote \strong{number of partition} of #{n} into #{k} parts by #{p_k(n)}.
}

\p{
  There is no convenient formula for the number #{p_k(n)}, but we have the following recursive formula:
  ##{
    p_k(n) = p_{k - 1}(n - 1) + p_k(n - k)
  }
  ##{
    p_k(n) = 0 \quad \text{if} \quad k > n
  }
}